TY  - JOUR
TI  - The Coefficient of Resource Utilization
AU  - Debreu, Gerard
AB  - [A numerical evaluation of the "dead loss" associated with a non-optimal situation (in the Pareto sense) of an economic system is sought. Use is made of the intrinsic price systems associated with optimal situations of whose existence a noncalculus proof is given. A coefficient of resource utilization yielding measures of the efficiency of the economy is introduced. The treatment is based on vector-set properties in the commodity space.]
C1  - Full publication date: Jul., 1951
DB  - JSTOR
DO  - 10.2307/1906814
